  * Check that `/tmp/crosshurd.[MACHINE]/etc/hosts` has been created correctly.

  * \# sudo umount /tmp/crosshurd.[MACHINE]  
    \# sudo rmdir /tmp/crosshurd.[MACHINE]

  * /etc/xen/[MACHINE]

  * \# xm create -c [MACHINE]

      * \# /install

